Barricader - (6)
- The barricader can protect people with 3 types of shield. 
-- The Divine Shield, protects the person for a night, and reveals the name of the attacker if they are attacked. It is Strong Protection.
-- The Strong Shield, protects the person for a night, and has no special effects. It is Strong Protection.
-- The Weak Shield, protects the person for a night, but kills you as well if the person is attacked. It is Weak Protection.
- Each of the shields can be used only once, regardless of if the person is attacked or not. Gets back all the shields if they die and respawn.
- Cannot use more than 1 shield every night. Can be role blocked. Protection is night end. Counts as a visting action.
- Respawns in 6 phases.
